'''Len Wein''' ([[June 12]], [[1940s#1948|1948]] &ndash; [[September 10]], [[2017]]) was an accredited [[Star Wars comic books|comic]] book author and editor for both [[Wikipedia:DC Comics|DC]] and [[Marvel Comics]], best known for creating Swamp Thing and the All-New X-Men, including Wolverine. He likewise contributed his talents to the independent comic book company, [[Blackthorne Publishing]].

